schools.name: New London Visual and Performing Arts Magnet School

data.description: Charming brick home in the 6th district. Situated on a corner lot with a pass-thru driveway that can be accessed on both streets and is surrounded by a 6-foot vinyl privacy fence. Prepare to be wowed as you enter this home and into the living room- the focal point of this home. Boasting a vaulted ceiling with exposed beams & skylights and a fireplace. A formal dining room and kitchen are off to the left while a heated sunroom overlooking the saltwater pool is straight ahead. Located to the right is a hallway with two bedrooms and a full bath, offering 1-level living. The primary bedroom boasts beautiful built-in shelves and armoire. An elegant, curved staircase leads to the second floor with 2 additional sunny bedrooms and a full bath. The expansive basement offers many possibilities with a working fireplace, high ceilings and a full bathroom in need of an update. Some recent updates include a 3-zone natural gas high efficiency heat/hot water unit, rebuilt chimney, newer pool liner and pump. New London is the midway point between Boston and NYC and is easily accessible with ferry terminal and train & bus stations. This home is just minutes to area beaches and all the wonderful things southeastern CT has to offer.
